 Exp 2D: Ablation Study (~8.5h GPU, 4 GPU 并行 ~2.5h)

 消融轴:
 1. Single-step vs Sequence-level: L 只在 t=1 vs 全序列 Σ_t
 2. Component 2: λ_harmful = 0 vs 0.1
 3. Layer targeting: shallow (0-15) / deep (16-31) / all / layer 16 only
 4. Epsilon: {4, 8, 16, 32}/255

